      <div class="block__section">
        <p>The aim of the Big Change fund is to help people move on from living on the street, and into long term support.</p>
        <p>A group of charities and organisations has teamed up to create a central fund which is used to provide homeless people with practical items they need to build new lives off the streets. The campaign encourages people who live in, work in or visit the city centre to donate money to the fund to help rough sleepers get off the streets, rather than giving money to people who are begging.</p>

        <p class="text-center">
          <a href="http://campaign.justgiving.com/charity/forevermanchester/bigchangemcr" class="btn btn--brand-e btn--full">
            <span class="btn__text">Donate to Big Change</span>
          </a>
        </p>
        <a href="http://campaign.justgiving.com/charity/forevermanchester/bigchangemcr" class="display-block">
          <figure class="logo">
            <img src="../../assets/img/justgiving.png" alt="Just Giving" />
          </figure>
        </a>
      </div>

      {{>divider class="is-hidden--smallscreen"}}

      <div class="block__section">
        <h2 class="h2">Where will my money go?</h2>
        <p>Money donated to the fund is distributed to individuals who are homeless - paying for deposits, training courses, clothes for a job interview, furnishing a new flat, purchasing crockery, pots and pans and bed linen, and transport to travel to new accommodation.</p>
      </div>

