              <li>White goods over &pound;100</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card__footer">
            <p>Agreed by the Big Change panel.</p>
            <p>Applications are reviewed by a panel made up of one representative from an established organisation, two representatives from COR member organisations, one ex-rough sleeper in long-term support; and one representative from CityCo.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
